headline: Introducing the Cognizant Enterprise Vibe Coding Blueprint: Services to Help Clients Accelerate AI-First Transformation
summary: Cognizant (NASDAQ: CTSH) announced the launch of the Cognizant® Enterprise Vibe Coding Blueprint, a suite of services and reusable IP that enables Global 2000 organizations to operationalize AI-assisted coding across technical and non-technical teams, securely and at scale.
